{"tid":1063882,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"新《倚天》小美人「小昭」登場 網民大讚Kabby嬌嫩氣質好「省鏡","createTime":"2019-03-16T06:12:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-07T10:35:32.000Z","uid":12558,"like":10,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"2d7603a872d31013d1a2787dfa0ba6c5f5ab9cda","tid":1063882,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T06:12:11.000Z","msg":"選角真係好重要呀！<br />\n<br />\n《倚天屠龍記2019》已經播到第18集，由香港演員許雅婷(Kabby)所演嘅「小昭」剛在第17集登場。怎料角色初登場就引來唔不少注目。<br />\n<br />\n許雅婷於1994年出生，早年擔任模特兒入行，樣貌身材不俗。曾在2015年與袁紫僑﹑簡淑兒及溫心組成女子組合「少女標本」。不過組合在香港發展一般，所以許雅婷轉往內地發展。<br />\n<br />\n許雅婷早前也有參加《美人魚》的演員海選，而且進入了最後7強。可惜她在戲中只有幾天戲份，不受重用。<br />\n<br />\n許雅婷亦參演過不少內地知名作品，例如《梔子花開》、《鬼谷門》及《愛情攻略》。她在內地已經稍有名氣，而今次更在《倚天屠龍記》飾演小昭。<br />\n<br />\n許雅婷眼大大面尖尖，有氣質之餘亦帶點稚氣，難怪會被網民大讚！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SU3Jd6S.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSU3Jd6S.png&h=6e329a0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8xWR7rT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8xWR7rT.png&h=bd7c11e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5KByBkd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5KByBkd.png&h=14fd9bab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/avGF0MU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FavGF0MU.png&h=030e67d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AxuHuFf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAxuHuFf.png&h=6f6c968b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UfyX20g.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUfyX20g.png&h=c61aa0c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gOMR7rW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgOMR7rW.png&h=de498787&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"761ab7ebc7f7f0e3618e0cb4fbe9452777c618f1","tid":1063882,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislik